{META_DATA}: (intimate)
{DIALOGUE}: C'mon, Lenny - we'll take a look down there together.
{DIALOGUE}: Then you'll know.
{DIALOGUE}: You'll know what you really are.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard glances fearfully at the door, then looks at Teddy.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He THRUSTS the barrel of his gun into Teddy's mouth and WE ARE AT THE SHOT FROM THE END OF THE OPENING SEQUENCE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Teddy panics, shaking his head, trying to talk around the metal, but GAGS just as Leonard pulls the trigger.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A SHOT rings out as we -
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
