{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 20 EXT. DISCOUNT INN ROOM 304 - DAY <<COLOUR SEQUENCE>>
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard, BROWN ENVELOPE in hand, finds the door to room 304.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 21 INT. DISCOUNT INN ROOM 304 - DAY <<COLOUR SEQUENCE>>
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard enters, looks around as if for the first time.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An anonymous motel room, except that tacked to one wall is a HAND-DRAWN CHART showing the layout of some streets, and stuck to the edges of the chart are POLAROID PHOTOGRAPHS, with ARROWS DRAWN from each photograph to a spot on the map.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard inspects the photos.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Some are buildings, some are people.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All have the HANDWRITTEN NOTES on the broad white strip underneath the image.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard gets Polaroids out of his pocket.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The first one is of the Discount Inn.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He STICKS it onto an already-squashed lump of blue tack at the end of an ARROW drawn from a location on the outskirts of town.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The second photo is a blurred shot of a Brunette turning in a doorway.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The name NATALIE is written under the picture.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard flips it over.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On the back are two handwritten messages.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The first one has been completely scribbled over, but the other one reads:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "SHE HAS ALSO LOST SOMEONE, SHE WILL HELP YOU OUT OF PITY"
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard nods, then sticks the photo to the chart.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He steps back looking over the Polaroids one by one: Natalie, Burt, Discount Inn, Teddy.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard sits at the desk and opens the BROWN ENVELOPE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He takes out a photocopy of a CAR REGISTRATION and a DRIVER'S LICENSE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Both are in the name of JOHN EDWARD GAMMELL, but when Leonard looks at the picture on the license, he recognizes the face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard moves back to his wall chart, finds the Polaroid of Teddy and compares it to the license photo.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEONARD (V.O.)
