{DIALOGUE}: It's complicated.
{DIALOGUE}: You might catch a sign but attach the wrong meaning to it.
{DIALOGUE}: If someone touches their nose while they're talking, experts will tell you it means they're lying.
{DIALOGUE}: It really means they're nervous, and people get nervous for all sorts of reasons.
