{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard looks up from the VODKA BOTTLE, sighs, rubs his face, then stands up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He SNIFFS at his armpit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He puts the empty bottle on the counter by the sink, then wearily UNDRESSES.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard, NAKED, looks in the mirror, then RUNS THE SHOWER then steps under it, shutting the PEBBLED PLASTIC STALL DOOR.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard SHOWERS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He turns the water off, then hears the DOOR BEING UNLOCKED.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard freezes, standing in the SHOWER STALL, NAKED and DRIPPING.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Through the distortion of the PEBBLED PLASTIC DOOR, Leonard sees a FIGURE enter the bathroom and start pissing into the toilet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The distorted Figure turns and approaches the shower stall, becoming clearer as it gets closer, then YANKS the door open.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It is Dodd (WITHOUT INJURIES).
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He is SHOCKED to see the naked Leonard.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard BURSTS out of the shower stall, SMASHING Dodd against the wall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dodd STRUGGLES around, grabbing at the SLIPPERY, naked Leonard.
