{DIALOGUE}: See, I have this condition.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TEDDY
{DIALOGUE}: Well, I hope it's not as serious as his, 'cos this guy's dead.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard CRACKS Teddy over the head with the FLOORBOARD.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TEDDY (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: FUCK, Lenny!
{DIALOGUE}: That fucking kills!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEONARD
{DIALOGUE}: Remember me again, huh?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard FRISKS him, pulling out a GUN and a POLICE BADGE.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEONARD (cont'd)
{DIALOGUE}: You're a cop.
{DIALOGUE}: A fucking cop.
{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MEMENTO Yellow Revisions - 9/29/99 109A.
{META_DATA}: 173 CONTINUED:
{CHARACTER_NAME}: TEDDY
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, and I helped you find the guy you were looking for -
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LEONARD
{DIALOGUE}: Get up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Teddy CRAWLS to his feet, RUBBING his head.
