{DIALOGUE}: I have to believe that when my eyes are closed, the world's still there.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Leonard CLOSES HIS EYES, driving blind.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Stay on Leonard, not seeing the road ahead, hearing cars whip past.
